    "collapsible_content_yGz6zz": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_kArc3q": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I claim discounts during your Boxing Week Mattress Sale?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Claiming your discount is easy! The advertised prices are already marked down and <strong>Boxing Week discounts</strong> are automatically applied at <strong>checkout</strong>, so you’ll see your savings instantly. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_G8wgPj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do coupons stack?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>No—coupons can’t be combined with other promos or bundles.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_pNpaj6": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the best Boxing Week mattress deals for 2025?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>The best Boxing Week mattress deals at Mattressville include up to <strong>60% off</strong> all products, including premium mattresses from top brands. Whether you’re looking for memory foam, hybrid, or luxury mattresses, our Boxing Day sale offers unbeatable discounts you won’t find any other time of the year.</p><p>All products are <strong>already marked down.</strong> If you need assistance, our team is happy to help!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_TT7RMq": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How much can I save during Mattressville’s Boxing Week Mattress Sale?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>During our <strong>Boxing Week Mattress Sale</strong>, get an additional 15% when you checkout. All products are already marked down for a total savings of up to <strong>60%</strong> </p><p>In addition to these steep discounts, we also offer exclusive deals like free local delivery on orders over $499. It’s the perfect opportunity to upgrade your sleep at a fraction of the price.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_HVCGiq": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Which mattress brands are on sale this Boxing Week?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We’re offering deep discounts on leading mattress brands, including:</p><ul><li><strong>Aireloom</strong></li><li><strong>Marshall</strong></li><li><strong>Hypnos</strong></li><li><strong>Sprout</strong></li><li><strong>Stearns & Foster</strong></li><li><strong>Tempur-Pedic</strong></li><li><strong>Kingsdown</strong></li><li><strong>Natura</strong></li><li><strong>Sealy</strong></li><li><strong>Serta</strong></li></ul><p><strong>...and more!</strong></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rDEkY4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When does Mattressville’s Boxing Week Mattress Sale start and end?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Our Boxing Week Mattress Sale is extended until January <strong>5th, 2026, </strong>while supplies last. To avoid missing out on your preferred mattress, we recommend shopping early—stock moves fast during Boxing Week sales.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_YMBLE8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I choose the right mattress during a sale?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>To find the perfect mattress, consider the following:</p><ul><li><strong>Sleeping Position:</strong> Side sleepers need softer mattresses; back and stomach sleepers benefit from firmer options.</li><li><strong>Budget:</strong> Our sale offers a range of options for every price point.</li><li><strong>Size:</strong> Choose a mattress that fits your room and sleep needs—Queen, King, or California King are popular picks.</li><li>TRY our <a href=\"/pages/mattress-matchmaker\" title=\"Mattress Matchmaker\">Mattress Matchmaker </a>shopping assistant </li></ul><p>If you’re unsure, our <strong>mattress experts</strong> are here to help online, over the phone, or in-person at our <strong>Mississauga showroom</strong>.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_K6TAQD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer free delivery or trial periods during the promo period?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! We offer <strong>free delivery on orders over $499</strong> during the sale. Additionally, all of our mattresses come with a <a href=\"/pages/90-day-comfort-guarantee\" title=\"90 Day Comfort Guarantee\"><strong>90-day Comfort Guarantee</strong></a>, allowing you to swap your mattress if it’s not the perfect fit. Visit our showroom or contact us online to learn more.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_e8ib6b": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What about returns?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Standard return policy applies unless noted. See full details here: <a href=\"https://mattressville.ca/pages/refund-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://mattressville.ca/pages/refund-policy\">Refund Policy </a></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
